Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra..._clock_latency(25.10)  timing_constra..._clock_latency(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_path_delay_exclude_check_delay_from_ignore_clock_la-
       tency

Syntax
       timing_constraint_path_delay_exclude_check_delay_from_ignore_clock_la-
       tency {true | false}

       Default: false

       Excludes check arc delays from slack computation.

       When  set  to  true,  the software excludes check arc delays from slack
       computation for paths constrained  by  the  set_max_delay/set_min_delay
       -ignore_clock_latency command.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

